    • RobotState

      public RobotState(double x, double y, double theta, double vx, double vy, double vTheta, double time, String name)
      Constructs a new RobotState.
      Parameters:
      x - The x position (meters).
      y - The y position (meters).
      theta - The angle (radians).
      vx - The x velocity (meters/second).
      vy - The y velocity (meters/second).
      vTheta - The angular velocity (radians/second).
      time - Timestamp of this position (seconds).
      name - name of this position. (ex: odometry pose, vision pose, etc.) ("Robot Position" is the default and is the one that is plotted in the GUI)
